x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-platinum-short-n-sweet-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-platinum-short-n-sweet-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-platinum-short-n-sweet-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)</a>的新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Short N&#39; Sweet</a> 》已获得官方白金认证。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) – “Short n&#39; Sweet”评论：一位新的流行公主的崛起</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位流行歌星在夏天发行了她的第六张唱片，其中包括流行单曲“Espresso”和“Please Please Please”。</p><p>截至周五（9月27日），这位歌手的最新专辑已获得美国唱片业协会白金认证，这意味着该唱片已售出超过100万张。</p><p>根据 RIAA 的<a href="https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&amp;se=sabrina+carpenter#search_section" target="_blank" rel="noopener">记录</a>，这也使《Short N&#39; Sweet》成为她第一张达到这一里程碑的专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797935" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797935" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797935" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sabrina-carpenter-VMAs-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3797935" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 于 2024 年 9 月 11 日出席纽约埃尔蒙特 UBS Arena 举行的 2024 年 MTV 视频音乐奖（图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/WireImage）</figcaption></figure><p>这位“Nonsense”歌手此前凭借单曲“Please Please Please”、“Espresso”、“Feather”、“Nonsense”和“Thumbs”获得了白金销量，而她的 2022 年专辑“Emails I Can&#39;t Send”于今年 3 月获得了白金销量年。</p><p> 《Short n&#39; Sweet》于 8 月发行时首次登上 Billboard 200 排行榜第一名，并连续三周保持榜首位置，这也是她首张登顶排行榜的唱片。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/sabrina-carpenter-official-chart-double-short-n-sweet-taste-oasis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜</a>，她还在英国排名第一，成为历史上第一位同时获得专辑和单曲（“Taste”）排名第一的女性艺术家。截至本周，《品味》已连续第五周位居第一。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_eFRLKyIyD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill=