翻唱</a>。</p><p>与此同时，粉丝们认为卡彭特和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">丽莎</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-think-that-sabrina-carpenter-is-collaborating-with-blackpinks-lisa-3797898">可能正在讨论即将进行的合作</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenters-short-n-sweet-has-gone-platinum-3797928">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 的《Short N&#39; Sweet》获得白金</a>销量后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
内莉·费塔多 (Nelly Furtado) 表示，杂志曾让她的“橄榄色皮肤”“变亮” https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-furtado-says-magazines-used-to-lighten-her-olive-skin-3797923?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nelly-furtado-says-magazines-用于提亮她的橄榄色皮肤Laura MolloySat, 28 Sep 2024 08:56:26 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3797923 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手说她对媒体设定的美丽标准感到“有点愤怒”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-furtado-says-magazines-used-to-lighten-her-olive-skin-3797923">内莉·费塔多 (Nelly Furtado) 表示，用来“美化”她“橄榄色皮肤”的杂志的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Nelly-Furtado.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nelly-furtado">Nelly Furtado</a>谈到了 2000 年代初期杂志在她的职业生涯中编辑照片的方式，称这些方式会“淡化”她的“橄榄色皮肤”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nelly-furtado-return-to-music-new-album-7-interview-3778195">耐莉·费塔多 (Nelly Furtado) 谈回归音乐：“有人告诉我，我需要重新回归”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://people.com/nelly-furtado-says-magazines-airbrush-lighten-skin-take-down-hips-earlys-2000s-exclusive-8718249" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>采访时，这位歌手表示，在她的早期职业生涯中，她在编辑图片中受到了“大量的修饰”。她还透露，一些出版物甚至会改变她的肤色，她说：“我有橄榄色皮肤，它们会让我的照片中的皮肤变亮很多。”</p><p>费塔多还分享了他们如何编辑她臀部的尺寸。 “他们总是会在社论中打断，”她说，这导致她对媒体设定的美容标准“有点愤怒”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3372809" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3372809" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3372809" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr.jpg" alt="内莉·费塔多" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-Furtado_Beyond-the-Valley_Saturday_Martin-Philbey-5562lr-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3372809" class="wp-caption-text">内莉·费塔多。图片来源：马丁·菲尔贝</figcaption></figure><p>然而，这位《Maneater》歌手表示，在那段时间得到家人的支持，她“感到非常幸运和幸福”。 “我身边一直有一个很好的团队，那就是家人，”她说。 “我周围的团队感觉非常可靠，并且真正关心我的最大利益。我认为我是在正确的环境下长大的。我妈妈真的很坚强，她妈妈、她妈妈、她妈妈也是如此——总的来说，这是一个非常母权制的家庭，两边都有我的祖母和曾祖母。</p><p> “所以我被赋予了一种非常坚实的自信感，我称之为。所以这对我来说是一个探索音乐行业的好工具。幸运的是，我从小就得到了来自我周围非常慈父般的人的非常可靠的建议。所以我很幸运，我是幸运者之一。”</p><p> Furtado 的最新专辑《7》于 9 月 20 日发行，这是她七年来的第一张录音室唱片。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nelly-furtado-return-to-music-new-album-7-interview-3778195">在<em>《NME》</em>发行前，她在接受《NME》采访时</a>表示：“我已经大约三年没有踏入工作室了，但有件事告诉我，我需要重返工作室。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nelly Furtado、Tove Lo、SG Lewis - Love Bites（展示器）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kf_TN7i4eUA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>今年早些时候，Furtado 表示，她认为与长期合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-furtado-thinks-she-and-timbaland-should-do-a-las-vegas-residency-for-loose-3778711">在拉斯维加斯驻场</a>会“非常有趣”。两人第一次合作是为了她 2006 年开创性的第三张专辑《Loose》。他们后来与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a>合作制作了 2007 年的热门歌曲《Give It To Me》，以及最近的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-timbaland-justin-timberlake-and-nelly-furtado-reunite-song-keep-going-up-3492129">去年的《Keep Going Up》</a> 。</p><p> 《Loose》为 Furtado 和 Timbaland 带来了众多热门歌曲，包括《Maneater》、《Promiscious》、《Say It Right》、《In God&#39;s Hands》和《All Good Things (Come To An End)》等歌曲。</p><p>她在接受<em>NME</em>采访时表示：“我认为 Timbaland 和我在拉斯维加斯驻场演出《Loose》会非常有趣。我们可以从头到尾播放这张专辑，因为我确实认为它捕捉到了我们当时所处的世界。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-furtado-says-magazines-used-to-lighten-her-olive-skin-3797923">内莉·费塔多 (Nelly Furtado) 表示，用来“美化”她“橄榄色皮肤”的杂志的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Bright Eyes 取消 2024 年所有剩余巡演日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-cancel-all-remaining-tour-dates-for-2024-3797920?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bright-eyes-cancel-all-remaining- 2024 年巡演日期Hollie GeraghtySat, 28 Sep 2024 08:32:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3797920 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="明亮眼睛的康纳·奥伯斯特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队透露主唱康纳·奥伯斯特的声乐状况“因过度唱歌而加剧，需要治疗和康复”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-cancel-all-remaining-tour-dates-for-2024-3797920">Bright Eyes 取消 2024 年所有剩余巡演日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="明亮眼睛的康纳·奥伯斯特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bright-eyes-shows-cancelled-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bright-eyes">Bright Eyes</a>取消了 2024 年所有剩余的巡演日期。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-conor-obserst-interviewnew-new-album-five-dice-all-threes-the-national-cat-power-elon-musk-3794330">新专辑《五个骰子，全部三个》的明亮眼睛，以及为什么“埃隆·马斯克是最大的狗屎之一”</a></strong></li></ul><p>美国独立摇滚乐队上周宣布，由于主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/conor-oberst">康纳·奥伯斯特</a>失声，他们将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-cancel-record-release-shows-after-conor-oberst-loses-voice-3795079">取消唱片发行</a>演出。</p><p>现在，该乐队表示，由于这位歌手持续存在的声音问题，这也适用于原定于今年剩余时间举行的所有演出。</p><p>他们在 Instagram 上发表声明称：“我们遗憾地宣布，我们将不得不取消今年剩余时间的演出。”</p><p>乐队原计划在奥克兰（10 月 11 日）、洛杉矶（12 日）和拉斯维加斯的 Best Friends Forever 音乐节（10 月 13 日）进行最后一场美国演出，随后于 11 月进行英国/欧洲巡演。</p><p> “我们爱我们的粉丝，对于无法参加这些节目感到非常失望。所有头条节目的门票都将在购买时退款，我们将随时向大家通报重新安排的计划。”</p><p>声明接着说：“在过去的一周里，康纳接受了多次测试，以确定他最近声音问题的原因。据了解，他的病情因过度唱歌而加剧，需要治疗和康复。</p><p> “我们相信，通过成功的治疗方案和持续的医疗护理，我们将能够在明年重返赛场。非常爱并感谢您的理解。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAb8M6Qt3Md/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background